  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare the efficacy, safety, pharmacokinetics, and
      immunogenicity in subjects retreated with visilizumab or placebo after a response in a prior
      visilizumab study.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
